description: OPEN HOUSE CANCELLED ACCEPTED OFFER! This updated bi-level unit (1st floor & garden) on South Boston’s east side is ideally located between East Broadway’s shops and restaurants and the Seaport/Waterfront/Innovation district. Offering a flexible layout, it features full bathrooms on both levels and a nearly 400 sq ft private patio—perfect for entertaining and pets in this pet-friendly two-unit building. The main level boasts hardwood floors, recessed lighting, and an open kitchen with granite counters, breakfast bar, new stainless appliances, and pantry. The lower level includes a bedroom with en-suite bath, and two walk-in closets,. Additional amenities include a private laundry area, utility room with ample storage, and a patio access.  Don’t miss this fantastic South Boston home!
